Sandy Spring Bank offers opportunities at all levels that allow you to be more than just an employee. It’s part of our rich tradition and strong culture. We are committed to our community because we all live, play and work here, too. We encourage every one of our team members to find his or her passion—and pursue it. We’ll even help you reinvent your career at Sandy Spring Bank. We value your contributions, especially as we continue to grow and make our community the best it can be.   





 


